Crafted with organic whole grains, real apple puree, and authentic apple pieces, these hearty, muffin-inspired oat cups are sprinkled with aromatic cinnamon and a delectable crumble topping for a truly bakery-style experience. Packed with nutritional benefits, these oat cups are a good source of fiber and vitamins C & D, making them a wholesome choice for busy mornings or midday snacking. Completely free from the top 9 allergens, gluten-free, and non-GMO verified, MadeGood Mornings Apple Crumble Oat Cups offer a delicious, inclusive breakfast solution that doesn't compromise on taste or nutrition.
